name: MOONVEMBER
description: Moonvember is a community memecoin on Solana blockchain, inspired by a massive trend in crypto that usually tends to happen in quarter four, historically having the most green months, starting in October (also called Uptober) and then continuing in November (called Moonvember) when altcoins and memecoins go parabolic putting green candles and new highs everyday, bringing massive gains for those who believed and diamond handed.
